issue.title: Merge pull request #1 from mishingo/master
issue.body: Load wallet on every page, beginning ENS integration

issue.title: Load wallet on every page, beginning ENS integration
issue.body:
Es5 require `demo-webify` on every page that needs the wallet, and call `clientInit` on mount to initialize the wallet.

ENS calls to register a new subname on `register/username.vue` work via `ethereum-ens` package.

Pending calls to `setContenthash` on `register/profile.vue`, which relies on newer calls in `@ensdomains/ui`
